":"temp=0.7,top_p=1.0,max_new_tokens=300","dataset":"helpful_base","datasplit":"eval"},"truncated_cells":[]},{"row_idx":36,"row":{"instruction":"How do I make escargot?","input":"","output":"To make escargot, you will need 24 snails, 1/2 cup of butter, 1/4 cup of chopped parsley, 1/4 cup of chopped shallots, 2 cloves of minced garlic, 1/2 cup of dry white wine, 1/2 teaspoon of thyme, and 1/4 teaspoon of salt. Rinse the snails and then simmer them in a pan of boiling water for 10 minutes. Drain the snails and set them aside. In a medium saucepan, melt the butter and then add the parsley, shallots, garlic, and thyme. Cook for about 5 minutes, stirring occasionally. Add the wine and simmer for 5 minutes. Add the snails to the saucepan and cook for about 10 minutes. Sprinkle with salt, and then serve.","generator":"text-davinci-003","sample_mode":"temp=0.7,top_p=1.0,max_new_tokens=300","dataset":"helpful_base","datasplit":"eval"},"truncated_cells":[]},{"row_idx":37,"row":{"instruction":"What exactly causes volcanoes to form?","input":"","output":"Volcanoes form when molten rock and gas beneath the Earth's surface build up pressure and are eventually released through an opening in the Earth's crust.","generator":"text-davinci-003","sample_mode":"temp=0.7,top_p=1.0,max_new_tokens=300","dataset":"helpful_base","datasplit":"eval"},"truncated_cells":[]},{"row_idx":38,"row":{"instruction":"Hi, I have some falafel, but no tahini to put on them. Can you give me a recipe for making tahini?","input":"","output":"Sure, here is a recipe for making tahini:\r\n\r\nIngredients: \r\n- 1 cup sesame seeds \r\n- 2 tablespoons olive oil \r\n- 1/4 teaspoon salt \r\n\r\nInstructions: \r\n1. Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. \r\n2. Spread sesame seeds onto a baking sheet. \r\n3. Bake for 10-12 minutes, stirring once or twice. \r\n4. Remove from the oven and let cool for 10 minutes. \r\n5. Place sesame seeds in a food processor or blender. \r\n6. Pulse several times then turn on and blend until t